snippet.title: Allan Simz
snippet.description: Through all my years of living, I have not seen a movie so perfect as to avoid any kind critique. Unfortunately this is the price of true art, this channel was established to critique movies, rant on certain trends in hollywood ( like the pushing of propaganda through movies) and also to just have fun with movies.....which is one of the purposes of film. So join me in my journey to find the perfect film and also to stay up to date with all news regarding movies.
